  └── db.query (database read)
      └── (any sub-operations)
```

## Validation
After adding spans:

```bash
# Type-check to verify imports
cd src/shared && npm run type-check

# Test span generation
cd src/covabot && npm test -- --grep 'span'

# Run application and check traces in observability stack
npm run dev:covabot
```

## Acceptance Criteria
- ✅ BaseRepository.query() emits db.query spans
- ✅ BaseRepository.execute() emits db.execute spans
- ✅ Spans include db.system, db.statement, db.param_count attributes
- ✅ Repository methods emit domain-specific spans
- ✅ Span assertions pass in tests
- ✅ Type-check passes
- ✅ No performance regression (spans are minimal overhead)</issue_description>

